'''Jorge Erdely Graham''' is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] [[theologian]], religious studies scholar,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://elsoldenayarit.mx/opinion/18803-sectas-y-minorias-religiosas-en-mexico|title=Sectas y Minorías Religiosas en México|publisher=El Sol de Nayarit|author=José Miguel Cuevas Delgadillo|date=April 4, 2013|accessdate=January 7, 2014}}</ref> and [[author]].<ref name=lavoz/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://elsoldenayarit.mx/opinion/18803-sectas-y-minorias-religiosas-en-mexico|title=Sectas y Minorías Religiosas en México|publisher=El Sol de Nayarit|author=José Miguel Cuevas Delgadillo|date=April 4, 2013|accessdate=December 5, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Carlos Garma Navarro|title=Buscando el espíritu: pentacostalismo en Iztapalapa y la ciudad de México|year=2004|publisher=Plaza y Valdés|isbn=978-970-722-280-9|page=262}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=A Growing Faith--and Outrage |first=Mary Beth |last=Sheridan |url=http://articles.latimes.com/1998/mar/10/news/mn-27361/6 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=10 March 1998 |accessdate=30 September 2013}}</ref>

He is associate editor<ref>http://www.editorialunilit.com/pages/eng/_autores1.php?vAut=438 Retrieved 20 September 2013</ref> of Revista Académica para el Estudio de las Religiones, a member of the [[American Academy of Religion]] and former director of Centro de Investigaciones del Instituto Cristiano de Mexico.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.revistaacademica.com/consejo.asp|title=Consejo Editorial: Dr. Jorge Erdely|publisher=Revista Academica para el Estudio de las Religiones|accessdate=December 5, 2014}}</ref>

He obtained a bachelor's degree in biological sciences from [[University of Mary Hardin–Baylor]] and a doctorate in philosophy from [[Janus University|Newport University]].<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Erdely Graham |first1=Jorge |year=2000 |title=Suicidios colectivos rituales: un análisis interdisciplinario |journal=Ciencia Ergo Sum |volume=7 |issue=1 |page=67 |publisher=[[Universidad Autónoma del Estado de México]] |issn=1405-0269 |url=http://www.redalyc.org/pdf/104/10401708.pdf |accessdate=2 September 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.cpec.ca.gov/completereports/2010reports/10-19.pdf | title = California Colleges and Universities, 2010 | accessdate = October 28, 2014}}</ref> Later, Erdely Graham completed a fellowship in Theology at the [[Graduate Theological Foundation]].<ref name=lavoz>{{cite web | url = http://www.oem.com.mx/lavozdelafrontera/notas/n2911761.htm | title = Para la reflexión católica | publisher = ''La Voz de la Frontera'' | date = 13 March 2013 | accessdate = 22 September 2014 | author = Verdugo, Jaime Pardo}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2002/may/12/mexico | title = Abuser priests go to Mexico for sanctuary | publisher = ''The Guardian'' | date = 11 May 2002 | accessdate = 22 September 2014 | author = Tuckman, Jo}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sectas.org/libro_votosdecastidad/votos_castidad_acercade.asp |title=Acerca de Los Autores |author=<!--Not stated--> |date= |website=www.sectas.org |publisher=Centro de Investigaciones del Instituto Cristiano de México |access-date=27 November 2018 |quote=Es Fellow de Oxford Theological Foundation}}</ref>

